-- Leighton Gets $617 Million Contract From Energy Resources to Expand Mine
-- Victoria Batchelor
-- 2010-07-14T23:08:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-14/leighton-gets-617-million-contract-from-energy-resources-to-expand-mine.html

          
          
             Leighton Asia has secured a A$700
million contract from Energy Resources LLC to expand production
capacity at the UHG coal mine in the South Gobi region of
Mongolia.  
          
          


  


        